spekt for omgivelsene. \u00bb, skriver Mor til tre.", "En leser med signaturen Aslak er av en annen oppfatning:", "\u00abHvis trangsynte l\u00e6rere skal fjerne alle ting de ikke liker ved elever, blir det fort tomt p\u00e5 skolen. L\u00e6rere har for\u00f8vrig irritert elever med kaffe, r\u00f8yk og hvitl\u00f8ks\u00e5nde i \u00e5rtier. litt m\u00e5 de t\u00e5le \u00e5 f\u00e5 tilbake\u00bb."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sortrondelag"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "eb50dec566c93a951201d473bd23d904e89cb7b337c53f0003ab63212ce87206"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-01-03T20:21:51.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Ungdomsskole\u00e6rer og \u00abr\u00e6vsprekk-motstander\u00bb Ole Bernt Ravlum h\u00f8ster stor st\u00f8tte p\u00e5 Facebook."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1248980.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/printscreen%20ravlum%20ingress"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/bede5f9da5e215ca496c096d19944b5da124fc4e.jpg?59923b23"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Hyller r\u00e6vsprekk- motstander p\u00e5 nett -adressa.no", "Les hele debatten her"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "bede5f9da5e215ca496c096d19944b5da124fc4e"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sortrondelag"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "facebook"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["erkl\u00e6rt krig", "personen", "l\u00e6rer", "forrige uke", "st\u00f8tte", "buksa", "elever"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["aslak", "mor